{"tid":395851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝岩先送杯野飲既伙記！","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T04:13:59.000Z","uid":34773,"like":776,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52749e437fd88a6ac1119738b4156bd8a743590d","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"岩先下午茶去食個tea,  一黎避開人多，二黎自己毒l唔想咁多人睇到。<br />\n<br />\n叫左個tea 28$ 野杯要另加5$, 諗諗下就唔要野飲順路減肥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伙記見我閃閃縮縮着得寒酸，遞左杯熱奶茶過我台面，粒聲都唔出(正常會講一講杯野飲名)<br />\n<br />\n個一刻好想喊，第一次試到香港人份人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一次深水埗mtr出面間麵包鋪。<br />\n前面大叔買早餐，兩罐咖啡加兩個包21$.<br />\n大叔得20$, 跟手話咁唔要一罐咖啡。<br />\n個收銀話： 你下次比番個差額la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗，如我住呢頭一世都幫趁佢。<br />\n做生意賺錢係重要，仲有好多野更重要。<br />\n<br />\n仲有次食茶記，個學生哥無帶錢，個掌櫃都係叫我下次先找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港地最珍貴係人情味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/152044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F152044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=2801f4a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"672acbc7ecf0a022a5c2c1902bfc7770db55e76c","tid":395851,"uid":58512,"like":379,"dislike":6,"score":373,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"熱飲唔洗加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918c659685ea8d2c81e685d734ad027a6435057a","tid":395851,"uid":63670,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱飲唔洗加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...."},{"pid":"0eed61009608592f841a268e9b02c634bc48c996","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱飲唔洗加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要+5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99c09a7690fb716b718a42658800812c656302a","tid":395851,"uid":907,"like":442,"dislike":0,"score":442,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"喂 其實杯野唔係比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c75559d55441c2ae3d8b1cb5a11f8305c902a46","tid":395851,"uid":77092,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b01d6b391c93d83d03975cb675a8a92e6b05c96","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂 其實杯野唔係比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伙記唔出聲，後面個台又無炸形，又無miss野杯"},{"pid":"f9d02515df35e5b0ed0fdef0e88f1d87c25232cb","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔要野飲就講啦閃乜撚野縮<br />\n感撚動啲咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我叫左唔飲野， 咁佢又隊埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70a75c99feed420d2ef414e676f558fca535d98","tid":395851,"uid":75115,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"比錯枱炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e3d83be8fb4d12257b39ae51a1d5e681ce06a9","tid":395851,"uid":37760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2d29008c77b750bc2f1d8e950a59716df6ecaa9","tid":395851,"uid":15620,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少"},{"pid":"a82d6954653c78c35a9550bf523c4d354f6d8c0d","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時水吧出錯都可以送比個客掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9380a4914fff2efe21bc1e9536533c54072bff04","tid":395851,"uid":24456,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"真心 你對面有無人 或者 你可能坐左人地個位...宜家農曆七月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d25a90bf2683d2f27b54553cefd7e0e56d93fe","tid":395851,"uid":54927,"like":30,"dislike":31,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"你真係好肉酸 將件事講成人情味"},{"pid":"c7546bf8bad7f3192906d5ce7da57fcee2db8e3f","tid":395851,"uid":76403,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時水吧出錯都可以送比個客掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已正評，不過下次可以諗清楚少少先貼相<br />\n而家香港地做好事都隨時俾人抽秤<br />\n我認為最好都係遮咗餐廳名先貼張單出嚟"},{"pid":"d57ec963ce3340faef7d130481b7a942811d5785","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你真係好肉酸 將件事講成人情味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚易動情"},{"pid":"c7e69eca8818e5a10795144f056be0205a5ed8db","tid":395851,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"一間會有人留言話自己小左杯野飲"},{"pid":"695ad8e8653d92f17c42208177ea9a63325e4c8d","tid":395851,"uid":11254,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"比錯就比錯喇 咪撚ON9喇你"},{"pid":"6b407c775ec0227fa10f608a177f2cfce8e54763","tid":395851,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心 你對面有無人 或者 你可能坐左人地個位...宜家農曆七月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n杯奶茶俾你定驚，你諗多咗"},{"pid":"fe511708a2e4e22d954410ed3704dbc9b280c657","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時水吧出錯都可以送比個客掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已正評，不過下次可以諗清楚少少先貼相<br />\n而家香港地做好事都隨時俾人抽秤<br />\n我認為最好都係遮咗餐廳名先貼張單出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通茶記仔， 咁我又唔係打手sell食物。"},{"pid":"490453eb8f9fa20e628b7e6ca52ded7a21f90b7c","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心 你對面有無人 或者 你可能坐左人地個位...宜家農曆七月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n杯奶茶俾你定驚，你諗多咗</blockquote><br />\n可能係，成間餐廳光猛， 係我個卡位無燈黑媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccc134597d3fb72817a0fa1d11ee7a96ec8003c","tid":395851,"uid":145076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"講到成件事好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30e70ee27a8eea1c5b8bee1d0656f217210dd67","tid":395851,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n有一次深水埗mtr出面間麵包鋪。<br />\n前面大叔買早餐，兩罐咖啡加兩個包21$.<br />\n大叔得20$, 跟手話咁唔要一罐咖啡。<br />\n個收銀話： 你下次比番個差額la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗，如我住呢頭一世都幫趁佢。<br />\n做生意賺錢係重要，仲有好多野更重要。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n係咪櫻桃麵包店"},{"pid":"e239e07427ec2c19a005a9d0e1104360fb44364e","tid":395851,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"就係你條仆街飲左唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da3895a575f502e6789bc8957cff6b7ed55ff94","tid":395851,"uid":109005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得之我叫左熱奶茶 佢冇俾我<br />\n原來你拎撚左我杯熱奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee0d8b254b9ceccdb7f968109e20d5af1da3c34","tid":395851,"uid":8000,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"有次返早, 清晨巴士黎,<br />\n我係趕上車既, 咁上到車個巴士司機都打算即刻開車啦,<br />\n係臨開車之際我拍個8達通落去發覺負左!<br />\n我就話&quot;等陣等陣, 唔好意思,負左 我想落返車&quot;<br />\n個司機冇出聲, 用手做左個掃既手勢,示意我行入去<br />\n<br />\n我個刻都幾窩心"},{"pid":"80614d512858b29bdfd15dd0e21f1416363431f1","tid":395851,"uid":70917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"學生哥無錢點解掌櫃要你找數？"},{"pid":"12b913d9df45b29099c793f952b070d9458e85dc","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得之我叫左熱奶茶 佢冇俾我<br />\n原來你拎撚左我杯熱奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伙記比我ga"},{"pid":"20bc3ee061e1574c8774160d574c5a2fa7006dc6","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有一次深水埗mtr出面間麵包鋪。<br />\n前面大叔買早餐，兩罐咖啡加兩個包21$.<br />\n大叔得20$, 跟手話咁唔要一罐咖啡。<br />\n個收銀話： 你下次比番個差額la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗，如我住呢頭一世都幫趁佢。<br />\n做生意賺錢係重要，仲有好多野更重要。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n係咪櫻桃麵包店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記錯，應該長沙灣"},{"pid":"b40c6c12c3c7ebd4994d0b86ccf87f23dc0e6c40","tid":395851,"uid":76403,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時水吧出錯都可以送比個客掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已正評，不過下次可以諗清楚少少先貼相<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家香港地做好事都隨時俾人抽秤</span><br />\n我認為最好都係遮咗餐廳名先貼張單出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通茶記仔， 咁我又唔係打手sell食物。</blockquote><br />\n既然唔係打手，咁更加唔需要貼名啦<br />\n你永遠唔知呢個世界存在幾多歹毒嘅人隨時想借機害人<br />\n遮名只有好處唔會有壞處<br />\n伙記送杯嘢飲係自覺嘅善心行為<br />\n希望你都同樣自覺地為伙記著想下"},{"pid":"3cd8991209132dbc416ccf2bc0d607e515f86514","tid":395851,"uid":56957,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以番嚟比番杯奶茶個差價<br />\n我番左幾日工杯野上錯枱搞錯左<br />\n發覺出錯個時你又飲緊唔敢同你講<br />\n啱先老細賣單收錢問我做乜計小杯野飲<br />\n比人屌到反皮<br />\n而家老細叫我係街到搵你番嚟唔係就抄我<br />\n你快啲過嚟啦唔該你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9515824a97246e1a57dc0b931ac29dfdf3cf58ad","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學生哥無錢點解掌櫃要你找數？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntypo , 叫佢下次找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3733d0a454bd1443db18651da3e57877a9389b9","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次返早, 清晨巴士黎,<br />\n我係趕上車既, 咁上到車個巴士司機都打算即刻開車啦,<br />\n係臨開車之際我拍個8達通落去發覺負左!<br />\n我就話&quot;等陣等陣, 唔好意思,負左 我想落返車&quot;<br />\n個司機冇出聲, 用手做左個掃既手勢,示意我行入去<br />\n<br />\n我個刻都幾窩心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭叮叮都試過，叫我下次比番"},{"pid":"a36f74f4b816833de7938c50ecdda06e1914cb50","tid":395851,"uid":74171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有次返早, 清晨巴士黎,<br />\n我係趕上車既, 咁上到車個巴士司機都打算即刻開車啦,<br />\n係臨開車之際我拍個8達通落去發覺負左!<br />\n我就話&quot;等陣等陣, 唔好意思,負左 我想落返車&quot;<br />\n個司機冇出聲, 用手做左個掃既手勢,示意我行入去<br />\n<br />\n我個刻都幾窩心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭叮叮都試過，叫我下次比番</blockquote><br />\n因為啲錢唔係入佢袋<br />\n你試下的士狗會唔會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6077f83b0e419738d7a4df131203869c702bc734","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有次返早, 清晨巴士黎,<br />\n我係趕上車既, 咁上到車個巴士司機都打算即刻開車啦,<br />\n係臨開車之際我拍個8達通落去發覺負左!<br />\n我就話&quot;等陣等陣, 唔好意思,負左 我想落返車&quot;<br />\n個司機冇出聲, 用手做左個掃既手勢,示意我行入去<br />\n<br />\n我個刻都幾窩心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭叮叮都試過，叫我下次比番</blockquote><br />\n因為啲錢唔係入佢袋<br />\n你試下的士狗會唔會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會考個時的士司機知我考試收少我幾蚊話祝我成功！"},{"pid":"b1d843aba182e0796e7cddd1767f916ceadd6db2","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可唔可以番嚟比番杯奶茶個差價<br />\n我番左幾日工杯野上錯枱搞錯左<br />\n發覺出錯個時你又飲緊唔敢同你講<br />\n啱先老細賣單收錢問我做乜計小杯野飲<br />\n比人屌到反皮<br />\n而家老細叫我係街到搵你番嚟唔係就抄我<br />\n你快啲過嚟啦唔該你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人慈既老闆先請到咁好既伙記，咁下次唔好啦~"},{"pid":"2a7814d1f4da0c9bb2b248ccac628f7a5f460d2a","tid":395851,"uid":38030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"沖咗成日嘢飲，手都就跛，諗住沖杯奶茶出嚟自己坐低飲吓，點知擺低去完個厠所出嚟杯嘢俾人飲咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e35ce070fd4ec997590c6