1,"uid":121240,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"我都試過 同男友食華星 但差一陣先到晚餐咪等多陣先叫 男友就叫下午茶<br />\n點知個呀叔比多碟火腿炒蛋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以為上錯枱同佢講 點知佢話比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰下好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a2dede51ebab2e408f3d5c356e14170c2ee303","tid":395851,"uid":2141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"早排係牛頭角街市想撘小巴去旺角<br />\n但我唔熟個頭啲路 又趕時間 就上錯去官塘小巴<br />\n落車嗰陣同司機講其實我想去旺角 佢就車返我過去旺角個小巴站到 仲冇收我車錢（牛頭角去官塘個程） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fdc8bb20aaa7318e017cb01f6be299bda0094d","tid":395851,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩打手都咁多正皮 連登發生咩事"},{"pid":"f2013c07ffe7a1c9c964ae99c07410896b90bf8b","tid":395851,"uid":5340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:36:47.000Z","msg":"試過冇錢嗌餐 淨係單嗌個腸粉 個伙記比左杯豆漿話請我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7ab0755bbba73f4c4fab0554ebf273b53d5f9e","tid":395851,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"就係你條仆街飲左我杯奶茶"},{"pid":"641564387e785d5182b2c8de78f7d587cf1be175","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜鳩打手都咁多正皮 連登發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撚有打手， 間野食正常，地方唔靚，服務正常，唔係特別平，重點有人情味"},{"pid":"3bc9b2c3ee02e69fe236c8ddfb11d967e48373fd","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後生一輩同部份呀叔呀嬸其實都係好有人情味<br />\n<br />\n至於點解成個香港咁人情冷暖feel既原因 係香港人口老化 太多廢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然有d廢老都有人情味，要大家keep住"},{"pid":"8cf2d611f00b088a158a8b8cff7279f542abc1af","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過冇錢嗌餐 淨係單嗌個腸粉 個伙記比左杯豆漿話請我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山卡拉鋪位賺又唔係多，真心打個和<br />\n益下街坊做回頭客仲好啦"},{"pid":"fe76149b6d10891567da50ad7ac3d54d8fdd73ec","tid":395851,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"比返人啦，送錯咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfc6cb17ee274fda19f7ea90496a94ac7d0fb75","tid":395851,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:03:10.000Z","msg":"伙記準備被炒"},{"pid":"6ffae6b6c1da3759683e461d1af92541774c4577","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比返人啦，送錯咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲左啦都， 總之送比我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db1575880cb3518a3810fec155bc5e7b7467c3c","tid":395851,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比返人啦，送錯咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲左啦都， 總之送比我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比坐你隔離果個飲瀨架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f509b1fe9f7f00dde9fdd1d5f6439d470270a1a","tid":395851,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"有試過食開既茶記無帶錢<br />\n同老闆娘講 佢話下次俾番就OK<br />\n點知我隔日去佢已經唔記得左<br />\n仲問我點解俾咁多"},{"pid":"41ec29a824a327971de5b5019446cd33f3b7284c","tid":395851,"