>佢點知你啱唔啱飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：唔飲奶所以唔飲奶茶 如果佢比我都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隨緣啦"},{"pid":"af0e438fb88fcab9a77ccd770480fa885e2e6054","tid":395851,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"咪FF咁多啦 比錯左咋"},{"pid":"6e933a4c4cd07482bce03955edb1ff853d76aab3","tid":395851,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"香港最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5829599dd5f1aabbd6028f54d0ea9e7d7f5f393f","tid":395851,"uid":119001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"原來我杯熱奶茶送錯咗比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e2388dc883db07be00b1b38422c35524b7affd","tid":395851,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌表錯情"},{"pid":"0f6ac00f1f34f6eec695b258160ddf8d7ebe03db","tid":395851,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個伙記就係咁比人炒咗,多得你唔少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一時水吧出錯都可以送比個客掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n杯野成本咪幾毫子"},{"pid":"6a12ebe7648c989a635445f4cfd05e08b472d6bc","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚最忌表錯情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger, 伙記表示： 我成日放錯枱比水吧屌出完又出"},{"pid":"04f2bc7915781a60190647a2c4e76521ba36facc","tid":395851,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"南山邨嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295d2925bfced72f5fe0e9e6851b44ef4d1def82","tid":395851,"uid":13248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"其實應該真係唔係俾你<br />\n做人應該誠實d 五蚊都貪點做大事？<br />\n現實中樓主應該係度縮到仆街既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0f359d2f0930271deef2197bab8cf9afc6ae05","tid":395851,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"都唔排除仲有呢D ON9仔既<br />\n百中無一咁囉"},{"pid":"d7e2e3432fbd8121986f19aab586d03f9880011d","tid":395851,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心 你對面有無人 或者 你可能坐左人地個位...宜家農曆七月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n杯奶茶俾你定驚，你諗多咗</blockquote><br />\n聽聞d 舊茶記大排檔最多尼家野，一到7月就番去回味"},{"pid":"3b7b33dfc53f5587b6578b7b00f4e13fdc9d2713","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實應該真係唔係俾你<br />\n做人應該誠實d 五蚊都貪點做大事？<br />\n現實中樓主應該係度縮到仆街既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中，超級度縮！<br />\n但係係記唔出聲(叫奶茶), 係想我低調接受好意，唔係高調等我話 (我無叫奶茶 +請我飲)<br />\n顧及我自尊心先咁做。<br />\n佢心理戲演繹得好好近付完美<br />\n相信唔係第一次雪中送炭<br />\n所以接佢呢次對手戲都好榮幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc83a4e17dbeb9af3110ac372db365ef6caf7ede","tid":395851,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"9成送錯"},{"pid":"a570715bfabbcbe6a17194e6e161a4320fee1567","tid":395851,"uid":4559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01bff30325464c50eac21d26c2de37a8ea0374a6","tid":395851,"uid":2766,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"講起就嬲喇<br />\n話說我開緊工遲左放飯<br />\n見個毒撚自己坐唔哎野飲 同枱又無人<br />\n諗住拿拿聲拎完杯熱奶茶埋枱<br />\n跟埋手頭上張單說放飯食伙食啦<br />\n屌你老味 轉個頭條仆街飲左我杯野<br />\n屌佢又費時佢唔比錢發嬲走<br />\n明明自己唔比錢哎野都扮野飲左我杯野<br />\n宜家d人真係賤到<br />\n<br />\n我杯熱奶茶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76da360313a38b72c8df5740cd31cc1d9e2570e2","tid":395851,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"細個買叉燒飯唔記得帶錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n老闆娘話得閒先比 仲送多罐汽水比我"},{"pid":"3d59dadb6fb181c55002f4b67eeb3945dd464897","tid":395851,"uid":19837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"以前樓下有間士多又係肯比我賒數<br />\n嗰陣學生哥有時唔夠錢冇野食又會請我食d小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人情味真係好warm"},{"pid":"63865bd668febba184890dfed1178c00d9594281","tid":395851,"uid":34031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"有次放工返去順便買菜<br />\n唔記得帶現金<br />\n因為周不時淨係帶卡返工<br />\n個老世都話下次比返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 第一次同唯一一次幫老母買菜"},{"pid":"aeef3ddec5fe366a7cf8ac42b0ced0f98da487a6","tid":395851,"uid":61902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"發現比錯枱，但見你飲左咪沖過杯比人<br />\n你個杯咪當跌左囉，成本都唔洗$1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣問你拎返/收錢搞到嘈交仲麻煩"},{"pid":"dc7743eed42f2a327ae768d65a003922d18bf518","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發現比錯枱，但見你飲左咪沖過杯比人<br />\n你個杯咪當跌左囉，成本都唔洗$1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣問你拎返/收錢搞到嘈交仲麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕無此事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地默默地送上我飲。<br />\n係低調處理的雪中送炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92229cf01260af47194ecd229f73d0822692322a","tid":395851,"uid":87964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"我樓下間士多<br />\n個2蚊黑左d都唔想收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f878cb798ed303d37884029b5146c4316614d93","tid":395851,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:18:47.000Z","msg":"點解個學生哥冇帶錢要你俾返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d348cd6976c5d5cd1799eeaefecf9fd5a2f96ff","tid":395851,"uid":94535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"完來就係你飲左我杯野"},{"pid":"d76fdd7657675371ae8ce9d1b0c46fad5a65cf54","tid":395851,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"杯熱檸茶比錯枱咋係度FF<br />\n成本幾分錢懶得同你計"},{"pid":"401dd9f7e3542941a2b525dc92cbcd913e16212c","tid":395851,"uid":133375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"隔離檯出錯野<br />\n見你乞衣咁<br />\n請你飲"},{"pid":"fa0269a1f6e7d2fcdb9e0ee2428d815877bc072b","tid":395851,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"平時返學食茶餐廳<br />\n有時夏天好快飲完杯野 問阿姨可唔可以比多杯可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熟到可以打電話去留位 成間野啲伙記都識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5845269483665144e4a5b528b673cc60107bb272","tid":395851,"uid":19923,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"有次去老麥，有個半醉俄妹用半咸淡叫麥樂雞，個經理問佢要6 pieces or 9 pieces, 點知個鬼妹聽唔明d香港口音，係咁白鴿眼個經理以為佢唔識英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個時候我起後面提個鬼妹人地問佢要6件定9件。<br />\n<br />\n最尾解決左件事之後個經理問我食乜，我拎定廿蚊叫左個芝孖但係佢唔肯收我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頓時好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84ffa31d6af979dce452e4f6eebcd0ff412b195","tid":395851,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩先下午茶去食個tea,  一黎避開人多，二黎自己毒l唔想咁多人睇到。<br />\n<br />\n叫左個tea 28$ 野杯要另加5$, 諗諗下就唔要野飲順路減肥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伙記見我閃閃縮縮着得寒酸，遞左杯熱奶茶過我台面，粒聲都唔出(正常會講一講杯野飲名)<br />\n<br />\n個一刻好想喊，第一次試到香港人份人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一次深水埗mtr出面間麵包鋪。<br />\n前面大叔買早餐，兩罐咖啡加兩個包21$.<br />\n大叔得20$, 跟手話咁唔要一罐咖啡。<br />\n個收銀話： 你下次比番個差額la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗，如我住呢頭一世都幫趁佢。<br />\n做生意賺錢係重要，仲有好多野更重要。<br />\n<br />\n仲有次食茶記，個學生哥無帶錢，個掌櫃都係叫我下次先找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以香港地最珍貴係人情味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/152044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F152044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=2801f4a2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正啊南豐 中學放晏成日去食 啲野係抵食夾大件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b0fd4f8b9e9d12a801ec9ab615f77cb822de6d","tid":395851,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"之前成日食飯果到 個阿姐次次都唔收我凍飲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a36295282b3782d711aac2afb1dbbdfb3a157","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前成日食飯果到 個阿姐次次都唔收我凍飲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwhy ge"},{"pid":"98332241d5dcfea59cdd184fcd2446f2cd7eef53","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解個學生哥冇帶錢要你俾返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntypo,  係佢"},{"pid":"33efe4af2b286434db3912163c3e6792b7fdbd52","tid":395851,"uid":86179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"細細個日日下午茶都跟屋企去南豐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起都有啲掛住收銀個叔叔，好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf72b91cb2757cb963f4f3d1269e6321a160efd","tid":395851,"uid":86179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個日日下午茶都跟屋企人去南豐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起都有啲掛住收銀個叔叔，好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"157bfea272c8d8c3bd7d1a442755a5b6055154a5","tid":395851,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"樓主應該唔係肥婆"},{"pid":"2fb75cab6eaed42cf59ad14d8a4a972c2f41279e","tid":395851,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"老個一輩好有人情味<br />\n後生個d 你死你事"},{"pid":"ddc51caaf0ca1a09e57790b14ac37277de61314b","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老個一輩好有人情味<br />\n後生個d 你死你事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家陣d錢字行頭埋沒良心<br />\n倫敦金，保險狗，美容雞。<br />\n為左錢就呃呃騙騙"},{"pid":"337d45fa9d5e1239161259068dfffe798116a62c","tid":395851,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主應該唔係肥婆</blockquote><br />\n女神"},{"pid":"33f5a44cd84ff041489177a4656a81623542a1a4","tid":395851,"u